<!-- ======= About Section ======= -->
<section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="row content">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <p>
                    Welcome to Sole Street Market – where passion for quality footwear meets the art of fashion. 
                    We are dedicated to bringing you a curated selection of shoes that blend style, comfort, and craftsmanship.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Expertly Curated Collection: Every pair is a blend of fashion-forward design and comfort.</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Global Fashion Insights: We stay ahead of trends by incorporating global fashion insights.</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Commitment to Sustainability: We prioritize ethical sourcing and eco-friendly practices.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 pt-4 pt-lg-0">
                <p>
                    At Sole Street Market, we are more than just a shoe store; we are a community of fashion enthusiasts and sustainability advocates. 
                    Our mission is to provide footwear that not only looks good but also feels good and does good. Join us on this journey of style and conscious consumerism.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section><!-- End  Section -->

<!-- ======= Features Section ======= -->
<section id="features" class="features">
