                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i>  We cater to all preferences, offering a mix of the latest hits and timeless staples.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            At Sole Street Market, our mission is to blend unparalleled dedication to excellence with a passion for distinctive footwear. 
                            We meticulously select each pair for its outstanding quality, unmatched comfort, and exceptional aesthetic appeal. 
                            Our commitment is to provide footwear that not only meets but exceeds the expectations of style-conscious customers.
                        </p>
