            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-2">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                        <h3> A Step Ahead: Envisioning the Future of Footwear at Sole Street Market</h3>
                        <p>
                            Sole Street Market envisions a world where footwear is not just a necessity but a statement of individuality and quality.
                            We strive to be at the forefront of fashion and comfort, setting trends and exceeding expectations.
                        </p>
                        <p class="fst-italic">
                            Our vision is centered around four key pillars:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Continuously introducing creative and trend-setting styles that define the future of footwear fashion.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Committing to environmentally responsible practices and materials, ensuring a greener future with every step.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Expanding our reach to bring diverse, world-class footwear to every corner of the globe.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Providing an exceptional shopping experience that values customer satisfaction above all.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2 text-center">
                        <img src="/img/Vision.png" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-3">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                        <h3>Core Values: The Foundation of Sole Street Market</h3>
                        <p>
                            At Sole Street Market, our values are the cornerstone of our business, guiding our actions and decisions. 
                            We believe in creating a culture that reflects our commitment to excellence, integrity, and innovation in the world of footwear.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Ensuring every pair of shoes meets the highest standards of craftsmanship and durability.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Upholding ethical sourcing and business practices, respecting people and the planet.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Embracing innovation and striving for excellence in all we do.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="fst-italic">
                            We are committed to excellence in every aspect. 
                            Our focus on quality craftsmanship, ethical practices, and constant innovation ensures every pair of shoes we offer is a testament to our dedication to our customers and the planet."
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2 text-center">
                        <img src="/img/value.png" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-4">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1 mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                        <h3>Connecting with Customers: Sole Street Market's Engagement Approach</h3>
                        <p>
                            We believe in building strong, lasting relationships with our customers. 
                            Our engagement strategy is centered around understanding and fulfilling the unique needs and preferences of each customer,
                            ensuring that every interaction with us is personalized, memorable, and exceeds expectations.
                        </p>
                        </p>
                        <p class="fst-italic">
                            We strive to understand and cater to individual preferences, ensuring a personalized and satisfying shopping experience that resonates with our patrons' unique styles and needs.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Offering tailored recommendations and services to meet individual customer preferences.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Ensuring prompt and effective communication channels for customer feedback and support.</li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i> Creating a vibrant and interactive online community through social media and our website.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 order-1 order-lg-2 text-center">
                        <img src="/img/customer.png" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
